name: Jimmy Fallon
monologue: According to a new report, the word that Donald Trump said most often in last week’s debate was “I'm.” The word he says the least: “Sorry.”

name: Jimmy Fallon
monologue: Rand Paul recently told reporters that his campaign is going to focus on taking down Donald Trump. Then Trump said, “I've tried it myself. It doesn't work.”

name: Jimmy Fallon
monologue: There are reports that Justin Bieber's next album will be released in November. As usual, Justin is expected to collaborate with a number of other artists including Skrillex, Diplo, A$AP Rocky, Flipcoin, 2 Chainz, Lowdown, and Rihanna. And yes, I just made up at least two of those names.
